data.description:
Over $36,000 in upgrades included in this price! One of our most popular floorplans with all the latest design trends. Top quality features including: kitchen and dining room popout, 3rd car garage, beautiful upgraded kitchen cabinets and Quartz countertops with stainless steel appliances, enlarged double deep Quartz kitchen island, Quartz dual vanity in master bath, stained wood railing, mudroom bench with hooks, craftsman elevation, upgraded carpet & flooring throughout, 2-tone paint, 95% high efficiency furnace and many more. Graham floor plan.

Listed by Prudential Utah Elite Real Estate
